  "instructions": [
    "Place a scoop of vanilla ice cream in the bottom of a large cazuela or individual glasses.",
    "Drizzle with a little caramel syrup and sprinkle with chopped almonds.",
    "Add a few mini marshmallows and a sprinkle of sea salt on top of the ice cream.",
    "Repeat the layers one more time, finishing with a scoop of whipped cream on top.",
    "Garnish with candy pieces, chopped nuts, and a sprinkle of flaky sea salt, if desired.",
    "Drizzle with a little more caramel syrup and honey, if desired.",
    "Optional: sprinkle with coconut flakes and chocolate chips for extra flavor and texture.",
    "Chill in the freezer for at least 30 minutes to allow the ice cream to firm up and the flavors to meld together."
